- cs.SD (Sound) is less likely but still possible as the paper focuses on end-to-end speech recognition.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SY (Systems and Control) are also possible categories as the paper proposes a new method for optimizing sequence models, which is relevant to both AI and control systems.
